{"tid":146499,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「烈火雄心」支持下消防班救火救人嘅兄弟姊妹","createTime":"2017-03-07T06:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T13:50:31.000Z","uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0d9468441649eab2c24cbc093684ff610a68f4e4","tid":146499,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T06:58:04.000Z","msg":"點解班<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">打人</span></span>警察犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就有無腦人士話籌款話撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但消防<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">救火救人</span></span>而殉職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個時班仆街政治人物去撚曬邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無做呢啲咁嘅大龍鳳幫殉職消防嘅遺孀籌款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地之後仲要生活，而且又少左家庭支柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班七驚坐完都仲有得出返來見屋企人丫，<br />\n消防呢，無咖啦，咩都無丫！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你班政治特警，憑咩可以有呢個待遇？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82369c5e5d02116b0d09677424804fa64045fd8","tid":146499,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T07:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FNr50Jf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNr50Jf.jpg&h=0f29cf2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n七警罪成並被判入獄2年後，除了有警察協會內部募捐外，亦有建制派人士籌組的敬言仁基金接受公眾捐款，幫助處理雨傘運動而受影響的警察及其家屬。而近日有前線消防人員透露，消防3個工會發出內部聯合通告，呼籲同袍捐款至敬言仁基金，引起部份前線不滿，批評作為紀律部隊「怎可明目張膽幫犯法的人？」，擔心影響消防處聲譽。有工會代表回應指，今次呼籲並非出於判斷七警對錯，只是源自同理心，協助受困的紀律部隊同袍。<br />\n七警俱已入獄，不少團體正為他們及其家屬籌款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/75812/-七警案-消防3工會籲捐款-前線批恐損形象-工會-出於同理心\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F75812%2F-%E4%B8%83%E8%AD%A6%E6%A1%88-%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B23%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83%E7%B1%B2%E6%8D%90%E6%AC%BE-%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E6%89%B9%E6%81%90%E6%90%8D%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1-%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83-%E5%87%BA%E6%96%BC%E5%90%8C%E7%90%86%E5%BF%83&d=GlETU%2Fuc5qoZzc1QHf9C2pUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=b8e7f1fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/75812/-七警案-消防3工會籲捐款-前線批恐損形象-工會-出於同理心</a>"},{"pid":"df1a4246e28cf662c24c2d816e48dfa946cb6a22","tid":146499,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T10:38:49.000Z","msg":"消防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53cf6e3cd91503a1d4ac24371292d6b7cf14eb4","tid":146499,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:30:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53cb2133b2b080b521cac6f9a0d3c79495e10330","tid":146499,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:50:31.000Z","msg":"之前D 市民咪捐左錢囉<br />\n<br />\n唔通又想再捐過??"}]}